SubjectCanadian Food Inspection Agency - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA that covers all employees in the Informatics (IN) Group Bargaining Unit, for the period beginning on June 1, 2022 and ending on May 31, 2026.
